Do iObjects.$define()
Do iObjects.$cols.$add("name",kCharacter,kSimplechar)
Do iObjects.$cols.$add("ref",kItemref)

Set reference iClassRef to iMethodEditors.classitem

Do iClassRef.$objs.$makelist($ref.$name,$ref) Returns iObjects
Do iObjects.$addbefore(1,"Class",iClassRef)

Calculate iObjects.$line as 1
Do $cinst.$redraw()